WEBVTT

00:04:57.992 --> 00:05:00.092
and they won't arrive
for another five weeks.

00:05:00.116 --> 00:05:04.381
The fact that we are stifled
with the most nonsensical laws out there.

00:05:05.219 --> 00:05:07.354
That's why we can't run businesses.

00:05:07.378 --> 00:05:09.520
It's like swimming through molasses.

00:05:09.544 --> 00:05:13.345
So, what can you do about that?

00:05:14.355 --> 00:05:18.022
I told you today that someone
said to me words that marked me,

00:05:18.046 --> 00:05:21.545
because I explained the same thing
to my employees in Senegal.

00:05:21.569 --> 00:05:24.082
And one of them started crying --
her name is Yahara.

00:05:24.106 --> 00:05:25.482
She started crying.

00:05:25.506 --> 00:05:26.911
I said, "Why are you crying?"

00:05:26.935 --> 00:05:30.460
She said, "I'm crying
